{{Infobox Theatre |name = The Lion & Unicorn Theatre |image = Lion and Unicorn Theatre.jpg |caption = The Lion & Unicorn Theatre |address = 42-44 Gaisford St, Kentish Town, NW5 2ED |city = London |capacity = 60 |type = Studio Theatre |website = [http://www.lionandunicorntheatre.co.uk www.lionandunicorntheatre.com] }}
'''The Lion & Unicorn Theatre''' is a studio theatre in [[Kentish Town]], [[London]], England. The Theatre is known for classical theatre, contemporary plays and new writing. The theatre is run and managed by Cutting The Strings Theatre Company.
